				<a href="/story?sid=33569">Firefox将屏蔽第三方Cookies</a>
			</h2>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="talk_time">
        <div class="icon_float">
        	<a href="/search?tid=39" title="Firefox"><img
						width="64" height="64"
						src="http://icon.solidot.org/images/topics/topicfirefox.gif"/></a>
        </div>
        <span class="user" id="19032">
